<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TEXT</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <h1>Example of font tag</h1>
        <p>Text is normal text without any font styling</p>
        <p style="color: blue;">Text with normal size and default face</p>
        <p style="color: green;"><big>Text with normal size and default face</big></p>
         <p style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;color: red;">
            <b>Text with Changed face</b></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
